irm is to provide high-quality accounting and tax services, with the goal of using our profession to serve our community. In the beginning of 2013, we merged with a reputable local CPA firm, Davis Chang, CPA, and formed Chang and Lin Accountancy, Corp. During this period, we specialized in foreign assets reporting and represented taxpayers in front of the Service, helping many taxpayers streamline their tax filing.\u00a0In the summer of 2019, we changed our name back to <span style=\"color: #800080;\">Agape CPA Firm<\/span>. We hope that continue to carry the passion that started in 2009.<\/p><p>Today, our tax and accounting professionals look forward to contributing our knowledge and experience to our valuable clients.\u00a0On this website, you can find articles written by Davis Chang, CPA and Yi Lin, CPA&#8211;as well as radio and TV interviews from the past years. We hope that these resources can help you to understand more complicated tax-related topics.\u00a0<span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">You can also scan the bar code below to join our Webchat or Line group.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-91b0a76 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"91b0a76\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-c6ca231\" data-id=\"c6ca231\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51a8440 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"51a8440\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div 